<h2>Newsletter Topics That Convert in Nursing</h2>

<h3>1. Travel Nurse Finance Weekly</h3>
<p>Weekly breakdown of: best-paying specialties this week, tax home protection reminders, per diem rate comparisons, and agency reviews. Monetize with: travel nurse agency affiliate programs ($200–$500 per placed nurse), travel tax service affiliates, and financial product placements.</p>

<h3>2. CRNA Insider</h3>
<p>Weekly intelligence for nurses on the CRNA path: program acceptance stats, interview prep tips, science prerequisite strategies, school spotlights. Monetize with: CRNA prep course affiliates (Apex, Valley, APEX Anesthesia — 20–40% commissions), consulting calls, and digital guides.</p>

<h3>3. ICU Evidence Digest</h3>
<p>A weekly summary of new critical care research translated into bedside-applicable language. This format builds authority fast in the critical care community and opens doors to CME platform sponsorships, nursing app affiliates, and paid subscription tiers for hospitals or nursing educators.</p>

<h3>4. Nurse Money Letter</h3>
<p>Biweekly financial guidance for nurses: sign-on bonus negotiation, travel nurse tax strategies, investing for nurses, side income legal structure. High-converting niche because the audience earns well and acts on financial advice. Monetize with: tax service affiliates, investment app affiliates (Fidelity, M1 Finance), and fee-only financial planner partnerships.</p>

