<strong>The 1,000 true fan rule applied to nursing:</strong> 1,000 nurses who trust you enough to pay $9/month = $9,000/month in recurring revenue — before sponsors, affiliates, or product sales. The challenge isn't building 1,000 fans. The challenge is finding the 1,000 right nurses and giving them something genuinely worth paying for.
